Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不得了啊 小可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.05,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雄鷹1號 請回話 雄鷹1號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在幹什麼 給我按測試計畫表來飛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 簡直像無頭蒼蠅嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底在幹什麼啊 那個野蠻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快看 第3追蹤攝影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會是他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雄鷹1號 高速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.96,0:08:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你幹了什麼？我重要的YF-19可不是玩具…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 剛才看到我的“龍鳥”了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【龍鳥】：行星伊甸上的特有生物，形似翼龍和鳥的結合體，背覆羽毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可是我從天上送給你的禮物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個野蠻人 聽我說話的時候認真點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是很喜歡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繪畫時間結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼該到約會的時間了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去和米拉德上校約會吧\N好了 他在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我們競爭對手的試飛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是試飛員？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.84,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男的是個瘟神 會給周圍的人帶來不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點去上校那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“做的太過火”是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.56,0:09:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把“挑戰”和“莽撞”放在同一個口袋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道是誰的名言嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的名言 也是我得到的教訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.24,0:09:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道自己的口袋裏還有什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是明白事理的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 開這麼快很危險吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.57,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.44,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不想和你一起殉情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很驚心動魄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個人還真怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶以前好像是森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去在附近爬山的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見了一隻翼龍吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【Paleontology】：翼龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.73,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩 你知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.40,0:10:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個“達爾馬提亞高中的可憐小子”就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.74,0:10:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 你早點說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那歌聲？不…不是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莎朗的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很快就要來這裏了 我很期待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點像我以前一個朋友的歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.32,0:11:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯定弄錯了 莎朗可不是人類哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是人類？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 管它呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.29,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 多謝大家今天光臨這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.90,0:12:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是“莎朗•艾普銀河之旅”的總監製 謬芳容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎各位提問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.94,0:12:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說莎朗超越了自己虛擬偶像的身份\N現在被譽為“最受歡迎的大眾情人”是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老闆雷蒙德還想收她作幹女兒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但另一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.19,0:12:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些專家說沒有感情的電腦歌聲\N只不過是毒品而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有的事 她要是聽到這種話會傷心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8}她的心思比人類還要細膩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.10,0:12:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,19那邊看起來亂七八糟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個亂畫的駕駛員被罰3天內禁止登機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來勝利要屬於我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好別小看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.81,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊裏的大部分人都賭我們會贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是難以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.58,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼各位 三天后\N我們在亞特蘭提斯圓頂劇場再見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的記者招待會就到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像是從這個星球出生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.92,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實你也想代替莎朗 用自己的嗓子來歌唱吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.57,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…我對唱歌已經沒有留戀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.64,0:13:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗還是未完成品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.78,0:13:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻已經俘虜了這麼多人的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.68,0:13:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果哪天莎朗覺醒後想要單幹的話\N我也就該退居二線了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.59,0:13:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要大家能得到感動 我就心滿意足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼她沒有覺醒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,系統明明都完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是…因為我的願望不夠強烈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.11,0:13:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太勉強自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苦惱時的你也很美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經很少見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.76,0:14:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過世的父親以前常去深山裏\N幫我摘這種名叫飛翔蘋果的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.77,0:14:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 其實這是人造花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.46,0:15:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼…會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在新聞裏看到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.20,0:15:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然到了伊甸 我想你一定會來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來的依然是個什麼都沒有的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都沒有的無聊地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什麼時候來伊甸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天剛到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七年沒回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道莎朗•艾普嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.24,0:16:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對虛擬偶像什麼的不感興趣吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.94,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在是銀河系NO.1歌手的監製
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣 我很成功吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.98,0:16:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的歌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.25,0:16:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很早以前就放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是新型機的試飛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.30,0:16:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在沙漠裏的新愛德華茲基地工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你能飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 這都是為了實現“在天空中自由飛翔”的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 你也很努力呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 你也來聽演唱會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.05,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能給你特等席哦 只需要濫用一下監製的職權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也剛做完演唱會的準備工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會成為最精彩的演唱會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.39,0:16:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的 莎朗是最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.73,0:17:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了 忘掉那時候說過的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會讓你忘記的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 有很多先來一步的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎？波曼主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了 勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.91,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把我忘記了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.62,0:17:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是學院祭的偶像謬小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.02,0:17:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你變成伽爾德的女人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是那麼愛假裝騎士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙 找上門來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.59,0:18:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虧你還有臉回伊甸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓給你的 不論謬還是計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.51,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手…住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個像過去一樣忘記我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.78,0:19:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我和你們認識的我不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和那個時候不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨你的便 但是計畫我不會放棄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.38,0:19:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓給你這種叛徒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心理回饋系統 運行良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【MENTAL FEEDBACK SYSTERM】：\N將觀眾的心理活動通過手環感測器回饋到主機上\N以此來瞭解觀眾的口味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.33,0:24:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閾下情緒效應 已滲入潛在意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.33,0:24:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【SUBLIMINAL EFFECT】：潛意識效應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.76,0:24:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,思想控制器切換至魅惑脈衝模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.85,0:24:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腦波OS脈衝達到Level-3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.48,0:25:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.92,0:25:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你這個臨時粉絲無關的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.02,0:25:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.33,0:25:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.31,0:25:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.88,0:25:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是程式錯誤？還是病毒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.00,0:25:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人發現會被抓起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.30,0:25:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 因為她是MACROSS財團開發的最尖端人工智慧系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.81,0:26:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入侵不了她 我也就不配當“駭客宅男”了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.91,0:26:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自以為是的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.56,0:26:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.23,0:26:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 你的心跳很混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.72,0:27:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來吧 莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.85,0:28:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個就是RF模組最後要更換的“撲克牌晶片”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.85,0:28:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【poker chip】：通指撲克籌碼，一種賭博用的代幣\N劇中應該是指像撲克一樣薄的晶片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.75,0:28:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直像是“隱德來希”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.75,0:28:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【entelechy】：亞里斯多德提出的哲學辭彙\N代表已達成目的、或將潛能變為現實的能動本源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.35,0:28:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不巧,我從來都沒認同過亞里斯多德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:30.59,0:28:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不相信他那句“靈魂與肉體是不可分離的”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:37.97,0:28:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是被你嚇了一跳 謬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.23,0:28:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然看到你是莎朗•艾普的經紀人還是什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:43.80,0:28:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是監製哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.81,0:28:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 是什麼都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.01,0:28:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱特你還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:52.78,0:28:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經是兩個孩子的母親了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.05,0:28:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你結婚了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.32,0:29:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你猜是跟誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.82,0:29:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在勇、伽爾德和摩根之中的誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.36,0:29:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摩根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.23,0:29:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:09.00,0:29:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶然見到過他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.27,0:29:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們倆也都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.54,0:29:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像都在新愛德華茲基地做試飛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.94,0:29:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 大家都實現了各自的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:25.75,0:29:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喲 好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.25,0:29:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摩根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:29.05,0:29:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不叫我媽來照看孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:31.52,0:29:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然回家了一次…但是她們剛好在賣舊貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.19,0:29:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果孩子們也被賣掉的話就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.03,0:29:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.26,0:29:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.00,0:29:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就開始模仿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.84,0:29:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.84,0:30:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼下一首就讓謬唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.32,0:30:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,期待很久了 學院祭的偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.79,0:30:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唱吧，就唱你以前作的那首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.62,0:30:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是叫做“VOICES”吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.79,0:30:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.03,0:30:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:18.50,0:30:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…已經不唱歌了 都已經畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.97,0:30:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我已經厭倦了唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.74,0:30:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在哪還能記得住以前的歌啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:29.04,0:30:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.38,0:30:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼由我來唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.68,0:30:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:38.05,0:30:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去解手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.56,0:30:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我 可以進去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.83,0:30:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我進來咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.77,0:31:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想問 “你究竟在做什麼”對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.41,0:31:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的“19”檢修完畢之前\N我要誘拐莎朗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.92,0:31:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 關鍵的部分就是出不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.05,0:31:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了 貞操可沒那麼容易到手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:17.99,0:31:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要把我和你混為一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.53,0:31:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在說感情程式的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.96,0:31:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說…這東西也許有智慧\N但它有心嗎？心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.21,0:31:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇 你在那邊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.88,0:31:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是米拉德大叔找我 就說我不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:40.85,0:31:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是女孩子打來的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.58,0:31:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那接過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.09,0:31:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂？ 凱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.09,0:31:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.32,0:31:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然知道我在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.06,0:31:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你從高中開始就暗戀我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.56,0:31:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是和以前一樣笨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:58.10,0:32:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又在牆上開洞了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.60,0:32:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的嘴巴還是那麼毒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.10,0:32:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我正和謬一起喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.31,0:32:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很奇怪啊 謬居然不唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:10.38,0:32:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不再唱了
