Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:23.74,0:59:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:25.34,0:59:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在我房裏做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:27.98,0:59:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要回地球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:31.25,0:59:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天就要離開伊甸 做好準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:35.72,0:59:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走的真急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:38.39,0:59:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MACROSS統合總部有聯絡過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:43.20,0:59:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邀請我們在這次宇宙大戰結束30周年\N紀念典禮中舉行演唱會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:50.64,0:59:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人工智慧完成了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:54.34,0:59:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球的演唱會中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:56.34,0:59:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就輪到真正的莎朗•艾普出場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.82,1:00:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想讓你留在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:11.16,1:00:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想讓你一直留在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:15.49,1:00:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為了保護你而活著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:19.06,1:00:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概從很久以前開始…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.04,1:00:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請收下這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:31.58,1:00:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.61,1:00:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下次見面之前 由你來保管它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.95,1:00:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我現在還沒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:54.23,1:00:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個詞語是夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.51,1:01:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將我心中沉睡的黑暗悄悄帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.40,1:01:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二個詞語是微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:35.71,1:01:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為我指引著方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:44.22,1:01:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我擺動翅膀飛向上帝的懷抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:59.10,1:02:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲傷的往事隨著時光流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.55,1:02:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要一上來就做危險的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:18.18,1:02:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在最終測試前如果再發生事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:21.55,1:02:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你說什麼都修不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:23.05,1:02:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心 我的身體無論變成什麼樣都能修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:27.79,1:02:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是說你 我擔心的是機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:30.90,1:02:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.13,1:02:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:36.10,1:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來 再去“疼愛”它一次好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.88,1:02:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:48.31,1:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼突然中止計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:51.45,1:02:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:54.39,1:02:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:56.09,1:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:57.42,1:02:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.59,1:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想犯侮辱長官罪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:00.56,1:03:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:01.43,1:03:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:02.69,1:03:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是統合軍從總部發來的指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:05.00,1:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指令？可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.70,1:03:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:11.24,1:03:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球秘密開發的無人戰鬥機已經完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:16.34,1:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無人戰鬥機？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:17.91,1:03:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說軍部選擇了裝有人工智慧的GHOST-X9
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:24.78,1:03:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍部指示要解除你們的一切職務
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:28.92,1:03:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是革職嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:30.42,1:03:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也不需要駕駛員了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:33.36,1:03:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校認為這樣真的好嗎 人類再也不能飛行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:38.13,1:03:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我一直以來所做的事有什麼意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:42.37,1:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我耗費在YF-19上的青春該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:46.47,1:03:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去和將軍理論
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:48.11,1:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他見識下駕駛員的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:49.81,1:03:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:54.45,1:03:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍部已經決定在地球舉行的宇宙大戰\N終結紀念典禮上發表這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:59.42,1:04:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再做丟人的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.59,1:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑戰結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:09.73,1:04:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.03,1:04:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:15.63,1:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她…謬小姐坐今早的宇宙航班回地球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:22.71,1:04:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天有你的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:25.64,1:04:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是她的朋友打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:27.98,1:04:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:31.55,1:04:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:33.25,1:04:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道自己沒那種權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:37.86,1:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直都是自由之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:10.56,1:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:19.57,1:05:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一條新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:22.87,1:05:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新統合宇宙政府發起的30周年紀念典禮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:27.04,1:05:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界都像為莎朗而癡狂了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:31.38,1:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做了什麼特別宣傳嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:36.45,1:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:38.15,1:05:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是理所當然的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:40.99,1:05:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快 夢想就會實現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:05.18,1:06:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:06.25,1:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都等得不耐煩了 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:09.18,1:06:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想闖入地球的典禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:10.92,1:06:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓GHOST大吃一驚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:15.02,1:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經裝好了超空間推進器
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:18.23,1:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會進入鬆弛睡眠狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:20.36,1:06:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在到達“地球絕對防禦圈”之前 請你叫醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:23.20,1:06:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 我能帶著個小鬼去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:27.94,1:06:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這種違反軍紀的事暴露了 會被判處死刑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:31.71,1:06:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下來我就會因為協助逃亡而被捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:35.31,1:06:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:37.11,1:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YF-19不是你一個人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:46.55,1:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼我都不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:03.00,1:07:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:03.77,1:07:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YES SIR!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:05.51,1:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？是機庫那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:19.39,1:07:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道 那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:22.92,1:07:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追擊導彈正大量接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:24.63,1:07:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎擊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:25.76,1:07:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有時間理它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:27.20,1:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用超空間航行擺脫它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:27.20,1:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【FOLD】:利用重力使空間扭曲重疊\N並借此進行長距離移動的超空間航行法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:28.66,1:07:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:29.70,1:07:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距超空間航行系統啟動還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:31.43,1:07:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5、4、3、2、1、0
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:43.44,1:07:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 已經進入超空間航行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:45.51,1:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通常戰機不可能追上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:47.28,1:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能追擊的只有YF-21
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:50.08,1:07:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我叫波曼出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.45,1:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是測試機由平民駕駛的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:54.79,1:07:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,責任由我來負
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:06.60,1:08:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你見謬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:23.99,1:08:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禁止入內是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:26.65,1:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是瑪姬先生吩咐我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:29.16,1:08:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓謬小姐你隨便接近的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:30.99,1:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對莎朗造成負面影響就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:34.16,1:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說不再需要我了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:36.40,1:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:37.30,1:08:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形式上有你在比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:40.17,1:08:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形式上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:41.80,1:08:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪姬在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:43.30,1:08:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:45.61,1:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼隨便解除謬的職務
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:48.38,1:08:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣莎朗怎麼運作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:52.78,1:08:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠生化神經晶片
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:52.78,1:08:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【BIO/NEURAL CHIP】：統合軍秘密開發的晶片\N能使AI具有自動學習機能，疑似與ghost x-9搭載的晶片相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:55.22,1:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:56.45,1:08:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗已經有了自我學習的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:58.92,1:09:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不怕犯法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:00.86,1:09:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是含有自我保存本能的可怕東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:04.19,1:09:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那本能增幅該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:06.09,1:09:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會產生無法預測的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:07.96,1:09:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是我們真正尋求的莎朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.90,1:09:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.37,1:09:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能控制的話有什麼用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:17.37,1:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演唱會要中止
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:19.07,1:09:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要立刻拆除晶片
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:34.82,1:09:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好 這裏是主控室
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:38.33,1:09:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏很快就會變成一個\N沒人在乎你死活的城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:43.80,1:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成只能看到莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.50,1:09:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能聽到莎朗聲音的城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:50.24,1:09:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切已開始向無法阻止的方向前進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:38.55,1:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:53.47,1:10:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球人和傑特拉帝人攜起手來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.21,1:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:05.35,1:11:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰來打開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:23.33,1:11:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人嗎 誰來救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:26.67,1:11:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:42.35,1:11:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.06,1:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經什麼都不用做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.16,1:12:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什麼都做不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:06.81,1:12:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:12.88,1:12:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:18.05,1:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是從你身上誕生出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.79,1:12:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是你的產物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:25.29,1:12:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且現在 我已經與你不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:31.33,1:12:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:40.61,1:12:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡伽爾德吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:45.11,1:12:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你更喜歡勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:49.98,1:12:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.09,1:12:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:05.86,1:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.23,1:14:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:09.70,1:14:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我依靠自己的心靈活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:11.53,1:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 你是由程式設計出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:14.70,1:14:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你相信自己有感情也是虛構出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:19.11,1:14:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你真的擁有自己的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:21.68,1:14:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道自己想做什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:24.31,1:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠自我思考、擁有心靈這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:28.22,1:14:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是瑪姬虛構出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:30.25,1:14:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為了實現自己的願望而活動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:35.92,1:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:38.46,1:14:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想看他高興的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:42.20,1:14:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他勇很快就會到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:46.43,1:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我已經不需要你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:52.81,1:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:28.58,1:15:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反應挺快的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:30.41,1:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我們也耍不了小花招
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:32.91,1:15:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有強行突破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:35.08,1:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸毀衛星軌道上的自動防衛衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:38.55,1:15:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁它們的碎片沖入大氣層燃燒起來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:41.16,1:15:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就混到那些碎片裏 沖進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:45.23,1:15:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候為了不被識別出機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:47.63,1:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要把操縱系統關掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:50.53,1:15:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的程式計算出來的最佳方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:55.24,1:15:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然計算出來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:56.80,1:15:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信你的計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:58.97,1:15:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:00.47,1:16:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信任我的技術吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:02.48,1:16:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候與技術無關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:04.48,1:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾乎是全靠運氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:07.01,1:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運氣也是技術的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:10.48,1:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就更加沒法信任你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:55.79,1:17:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:59.09,1:18:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太美了 莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:02.00,1:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 用那光輝照耀未來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:49.54,1:18:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不如讓我飛過去比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:54.48,1:18:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也曾任性的偷走過機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:57.22,1:19:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官們為了幫我掩蓋證據費了很大力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:01.99,1:19:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來這次輪到我幫別人來掩蓋證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:04.99,1:19:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:08.70,1:19:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情地去飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:23.21,1:19:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來能趕的上約會時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:42.46,1:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:43.80,1:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:45.20,1:19:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:46.33,1:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本應該由你變成灰燼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:48.97,1:19:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 陰險的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:51.00,1:19:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是在別人背後打轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:03.55,1:20:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒時間陪你這個白癡玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:25.44,1:20:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你總是要妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:32.44,1:20:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:58.94,1:20:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從小時候起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:00.31,1:21:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就總是跟在我後面打轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:03.38,1:21:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人的屁股你也窮追不捨
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:05.78,1:21:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:06.98,1:21:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元旦那天的“懦夫博弈”也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:06.98,1:21:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【chicken race】：一種遊戲，也被稱作鬥雞博弈（chicken game）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:09.28,1:21:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是我贏了 你還要胡攪蠻纏
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:12.79,1:21:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你的腳先往後退的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:16.66,1:21:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想翻舊帳嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.16,1:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的“GUNS”CDV車
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.16,1:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【CDV】：微型廂式車的簡稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:23.86,1:21:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到現在還沒有還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:30.17,1:21:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你自己七年前隨便弄丟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:36.68,1:21:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高中時我請了你兩次午飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:43.68,1:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我請了你十三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:46.72,1:21:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你算的很清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:28.33,1:22:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學院祭的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:29.86,1:22:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毀掉我飛機的肯定也是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:33.03,1:22:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬼才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:33.73,1:22:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別裝傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:39.34,1:22:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙真可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:09.44,1:23:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:12.37,1:23:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不管什麼時候\N都要毀掉我重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.65,1:23:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:20.61,1:23:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:24.55,1:23:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:41.03,1:23:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七年前那個時候也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:46.01,1:23:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:54.35,1:23:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是你在那裏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:01.48,1:25:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:04.62,1:25:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把一切都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:09.26,1:25:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後我把自己的記憶鎖了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:15.20,1:25:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我失去他了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:19.70,1:25:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為恢復真正記憶的代價
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:24.90,1:25:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我壞掉了嗎…瘋了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:49.53,1:25:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:52.93,1:25:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然的咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:59.44,1:26:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別太當真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:01.91,1:26:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小時候我們不是經常玩人力飛機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:05.55,1:26:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關掉引擎 隨風翱翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:11.02,1:26:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我管這叫做“必殺龍鳥猛襲”
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:39.21,1:26:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該知道以前的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:45.05,1:26:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:47.32,1:26:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直被我罵成是叛徒、卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:53.49,1:26:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謬她也知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:57.83,1:27:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們可憐我這個傑特拉帝人 故意瞞著我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:01.50,1:27:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上中學的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:04.90,1:27:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我毀掉了你製作的飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:08.48,1:27:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.71,1:27:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為它做的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:11.64,1:27:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想試飛一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:13.75,1:27:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:16.52,1:27:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把過去的事都忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:23.89,1:27:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:28.19,1:27:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯定還有瞞著我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:30.30,1:27:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:54.39,1:27:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到頭來 他們還是很要好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:06.70,1:28:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:12.41,1:28:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:17.41,1:28:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GHOST嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:19.05,1:28:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於碰到它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:20.98,1:28:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:24.22,1:28:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:25.08,1:28:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的約會物件 你別出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:27.85,1:28:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的臺詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:29.62,1:28:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌聲難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:58.49,1:28:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:00.92,1:29:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她連MACROSS號的主電腦都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:03.99,1:29:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇 我在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:08.50,1:29:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:10.80,1:29:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這東西在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:13.13,1:29:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她完全失控了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:15.13,1:29:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GHOST也被莎朗控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:17.67,1:29:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:18.74,1:29:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在等你 勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:21.01,1:29:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只等你一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:22.64,1:29:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謬…謬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:24.78,1:29:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她只是一個空殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:26.65,1:29:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把歌唱和愛情都交托給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:30.38,1:29:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她腦內只剩下一片空白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:32.15,1:29:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:33.15,1:29:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:34.65,1:29:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對謬怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:39.43,1:29:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你們 請救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:54.54,1:29:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒人能分開我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:58.28,1:29:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:00.05,1:30:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:00.88,1:30:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:01.92,1:30:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪物由我來對付
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:03.58,1:30:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去謬那裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:05.55,1:30:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:20.00,1:30:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論何時都要保護謬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:21.83,1:30:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我們的誓言吧
