Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:11.42,1:31:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣做或許更明智
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:13.62,1:31:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你也這樣說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:15.96,1:31:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別慢吞吞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:20.39,1:31:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真氣人 一個個的都這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:25.13,1:31:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後可別哭著求我啊
