Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:19.91,1:33:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像記起來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:25.55,1:33:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續接近有危險 可能是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:28.25,1:33:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴 正合我意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:36.13,1:33:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥、受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:40.50,1:33:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我繼承了你內心深處的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:46.54,1:33:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你收藏起來的一切感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:05.86,1:34:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:08.36,1:34:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:09.36,1:34:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗把MACROSS佔據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:10.90,1:34:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:12.37,1:34:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想制止莎朗就要破壞MACROSS的情報網絡中樞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:16.60,1:34:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:17.70,1:34:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心臟部分在…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:23.78,1:34:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:28.38,1:34:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇已經是我的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:40.19,1:34:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了 要害在主天線後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:43.70,1:34:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正下方13-D
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:52.81,1:34:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇！是勇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:58.08,1:34:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:01.15,1:35:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:05.42,1:35:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃
