Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:24.10,1:35:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把病毒輸入莎朗的網路 讓她混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:28.44,1:35:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做的到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:29.74,1:35:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明知故問
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:30.74,1:35:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:32.48,1:35:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:12.25,1:36:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:14.69,1:36:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:24.53,1:36:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你所希望的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:27.30,1:36:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:29.34,1:36:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給予這世上每個人應有的感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:35.24,1:36:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實現愛人的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:39.08,1:36:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給他最大的感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:41.15,1:36:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是自己活下去的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:51.72,1:36:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里會有啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:53.49,1:36:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:55.16,1:36:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種傻乎乎的感動哪里都不會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:03.30,1:37:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇追求的是遙遠的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:07.54,1:37:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拼命挑戰天空時
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:10.24,1:37:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生死之間窺見的感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:15.92,1:37:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想讓勇體會到那種感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:22.36,1:37:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怕了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:24.76,1:37:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢承認勇對藍天的愛更勝於你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:37.40,1:37:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什麼也不用做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:43.31,1:37:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:47.78,1:37:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:01.49,1:38:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:02.80,1:38:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有解除限制器 發揮極限性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:09.50,1:38:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇 情況如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:13.31,1:38:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德嗎 情況很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:16.14,1:38:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到謬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:18.41,1:38:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:21.78,1:38:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還沒對你說過吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:26.19,1:38:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:28.85,1:38:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這邊很快就可以處理妥當
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:31.66,1:38:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結束之後我很想跟你喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:33.69,1:38:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:35.39,1:38:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了慶祝我們久別七年的重逢…乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:40.37,1:38:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就先走一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:43.47,1:38:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:57.18,1:39:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽爾德 伽爾德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:41.86,1:39:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還剩一分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:47.63,1:39:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:03.78,1:41:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 很快就能接上莎朗
