Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:50.64,1:44:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:12.52,1:45:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個詞語是夢想
