Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:51.41,1:48:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想讓他看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:02.65,1:49:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那麼的愛勇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:11.10,1:49:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇能看得到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:14.83,1:49:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:17.87,1:49:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你搞錯了方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:22.71,1:49:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯了一個無法挽回的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:27.18,1:49:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我肯定也和你一樣…
