Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:25.50,1:50:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺像是作了一個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:29.37,1:50:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢？
