Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:56.54,1:51:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將我心中沉睡的黑暗悄悄釋放
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:11.72,1:51:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獻給你 我們未來的拓荒者
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:17.96,1:51:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二個詞語是風
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:24.73,1:51:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指引著我前進的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:31.67,1:51:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我擺動翅膀飛向神的懷抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:44.82,1:51:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲傷的往事 隨著時光流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:58.60,1:52:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金色的蘋果又有一個掉在我身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:13.41,1:52:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那從未見過的風景 就是我的歸宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:27.56,1:52:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為到達那裏 我願耗盡一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:48.85,1:53:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的魔法書 寂靜的月夜拉開帷幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:06.90,1:53:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懷著某天終將與你相逢的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:21.55,1:53:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,WE CAN FLY
