Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:34.99,1:53:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,CALL ME FROM SO FAR
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:41.37,1:53:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,THROUGH THE WIND IN THE LIGHT
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:56.55,1:54:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三個詞語是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:04.29,1:54:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果仔細傾聽的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:11.96,1:54:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你顫抖的雙臂
